A person sitting cross-legged in meditation pose, viewed from behind, with seven glowing orbs of light arranged vertically along their spine, each orb emanating a different color of the rainbow spectrum from deep red at the base through orange, yellow, green, blue, indigo, to violet at the crown. The figure is surrounded by soft, ethereal mist in a twilight forest clearing. Translucent crystal formations emerge from the ground around them, refracting the chakra colors into prismatic light patterns. Fireflies drift lazily through the scene. The atmosphere is deeply peaceful and mystical, with a sense of gentle healing energy permeating the air. Studio Ghibli style with soft watercolor textures, delicate linework, and that signature dreamlike quality of hand-painted animation, warm yet serene color palette.
